[ti:Infinite Love]
[al: 《Infinite Love》]
[00:14.50]They say that time is never really time at all
[00:20.50]That pictures fall and fade and crumble
[00:24.50]Nothing good can last forever
[00:30.10]Bright lights fill the sky
[00:32.22]Diving in emotions I swim through the night
[00:33.93]In darkness we collide
[00:35.66]Moving in slow motion as we survive
[00:37.68]They're gonna break us into pieces
[00:39.36]If we ever try to be alone
[00:44.26]No one to stop me
[00:46.10]From wanting to love you
[00:47.95]My heart travels at the speed of light
[00:51.61]To see your face
[00:53.56]Ignite the stars
[00:55.96]Tonight
